# DevFlow repository .gitignore
#
# The global gitignore (~/.gitignore_global) installed by DevFlow ignores
# .agents/ and .github/instructions/devflow-* in ALL repositories, so that
# DevFlow files don't accidentally pollute user projects.
#
# This .gitignore overrides those global rules for THIS repository (the
# DevFlow source itself), so that all skill files, shared rules, auxiliary
# files, and prompt files are properly version-controlled.

# ── Override global DevFlow ignores for this repo ────────────────────────────

# Include ALL .agents/ content (skills, shared/, auxiliary files)
!.agents/
!.agents/**

# Include all DevFlow prompt files
!.github/
!.github/prompts/
!.github/prompts/devflow*.prompt.md

# Include all DevFlow instruction files
!.github/instructions/
!.github/instructions/devflow-*.instructions.md

# ── Standard ignores for this repo ───────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.DS_Store
*.log
dist/
.env
